item.title: Compiler error!
item.dc:creator: @Avalon Avalon
item.description:
@Avalon wrote:

  1. “cooking” is an instance of the int[] class, and your trying to invoke different methods and variables which don’t exist there.

  2. atObjectX, atObjectY haven’t been declared yet.
